{"tid":2178182,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"安倍晉三辭職","createTime":"2020-08-28T08:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T08:29:50.000Z","uid":225950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61b3752400d159dcdbc557350250a70ed124c24f","tid":2178182,"uid":225950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:23:42.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三因為健康惡化，周四下午召開記者會正式宣佈辭職。他上月中開始健康惡化，8月確認潰瘍性大腸炎復發，不希望自己的病造成錯誤的政策決定而辭職。據稍早《產經新聞》引述知情人士透露，安倍請辭後不會指派代理人，會「請辭待命」留到選出下任首相後再交棒。<br />\n<br />\n安倍晉三近期的健康情況引人關注，安倍上周一早上突然到東京慶應大學醫院，7.5小時後出院。當時有報道引述多名最近見過安倍的人指，安倍近期感到疲累。日本一本周刊報道，安倍上月6日曾在官邸辦公室吐血。到8月24日安倍再到醫院，日本電視台報道，安倍入院是治療慢性疾病，他逗留3.5小時後離開醫院返回辦公室。日本放送協會報道，安倍晉三多年來患潰瘍性結腸炎(ulcerative colitis)，不希望因為他的健康惡化，而影響到政府運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200828/GGIKXCJHJRCDRF7TGBY2BLRTQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200828%2FGGIKXCJHJRCDRF7TGBY2BLRTQU%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=65372e59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200828%2FGGIKXCJHJRCDRF7TGBY2BLRTQU%2F&h=d293ffdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200828/GGIKXCJHJRCDRF7TGBY2BLRTQU/</a>"},{"pid":"7cf1106dd34c1aae78607eb79d3320633d9a93c5","tid":2178182,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"到麻生返兜啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qiX1Jemggwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqiX1Jemggwg&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=d4406917\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qiX1Jemggwg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XcAnSricnUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXcAnSricnUk&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28Xy